'''2014年白沙瓦學校襲擊事件'''，是指2014年12月16日在[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]西北部城市[[白沙瓦|白沙瓦]]一間軍人子女就讀的學校发生的恐怖襲擊事件。七名屬於[[巴基斯坦塔利班运动|巴基斯坦塔利班运动]]的持槍恐怖份子進入一個由軍方開辦的公立學校對學生及教職員亂槍掃射。<ref name=BBC/><ref name="20 killed, 38 injured in attack on Peshawar school">{{cite web | url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/807564/gunmen-target-school-in-peshawar/ | title=Peshawar school hostage crisis updates | publisher=The Express Tribune | date=2014-12-16 | accessdate=2014-12-16 | archive-date=2019-01-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190109173539/https://tribune.com.pk/story/807564/gunmen-target-school-in-peshawar/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>事件總共造成最少141人死亡，包括132名10歲至18歲之間的學生及9名教職員。<ref name=BBC>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-30491435 | title=Pakistan Taliban kill scores in Peshawar school massacre | publisher=BBC News | date=2014-12-16 | accessdate=2014-12-16 | archive-date=2019-01-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106221614/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-30491435 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Independent">{{cite news |last=Popham |first=Peter |date=2014-12-16 |title=Peshawar school attack: 'I will never forget the black boots...It was like death approaching me' |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/peshawar-school-attack-i-will-never-forget-the-black-bootsit-was-like-death-approaching-me-9929563.html |newspaper=The Independent |location= |accessdate=2014-12-16 |archive-date=2019-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106221427/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/peshawar-school-attack-i-will-never-forget-the-black-bootsit-was-like-death-approaching-me-9929563.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Samaa News">{{cite web | url=http://www.samaa.tv/pakistan/16-Dec-2014/gunmen-attack-army-school-in-peshawar-two-kids-injured | title=26 killed as terrorists attack Peshawar school | publisher=Samaa News | date=2014-12-16 | accessdate=2014-12-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141216140003/http://www.samaa.tv/pakistan/16-Dec-2014/gunmen-attack-army-school-in-peshawar-two-kids-injured | archive-date=2014-12-16 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>最少114人據報受傷並被分別送往Combined Military Hospital及Lady Reading Hospital治理。超過950名師生及職員被趕到的巴國軍隊拯救。<ref name="Dawn">{{cite news | title=Terrorists had no intention of taking hostages: ISPR | url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1151229/terrorists-had-no-intention-of-taking-hostages-ispr | publisher=Dawn | date=2014-12-16 | accessdate=2014-12-16 | archive-date=2014-12-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141216224101/http://www.dawn.com/news/1151229/terrorists-had-no-intention-of-taking-hostages-ispr | dead-url=no }}</ref>行動在同日傍晚結束，全部七名恐怖份子均伏诛。<ref name="The Express Tribune">{{cite web | url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/807564/gunmen-target-school-in-peshawar/ | title=Peshawar school attack: Pakistan authorities claim all Taliban attackers are dead | publisher=The Express Tribune | accessdate=2014-12-16 | archive-date=2019-01-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190109173539/https://tribune.com.pk/story/807564/gunmen-target-school-in-peshawar/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

此次襲擊是巴基斯坦自從2007年卡拉奇炸彈襲擊事件以來死傷最嚴重的恐怖襲擊事件。<ref name="CNN">{{cite news|title=At least 126, mostly children, slaughtered as Taliban storm Pakistan school|url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/12/16/world/asia/pakistan-peshawar-school-attack/|accessdate=2014-12-16|publisher=''CNN''|date=2014-12-16|archive-date=2014-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219110208/http://www.cnn.com/2014/12/16/world/asia/pakistan-peshawar-school-attack/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 背景 ==
{{main|巴基斯坦西北部战争|利剑行动|开博尔1号行动}}
位于瓦尔沙路的[[白沙瓦陆军公学|陆军公学]]，是巴基斯坦陆军公学和大学系统146所学校之一<ref name="Newsweek Pakistan">{{cite web | url=http://newsweekpakistan.com/taliban-attack-army-run-school-in-peshawar/ | title=TALIBAN ATTACK ARMY-RUN SCHOOL IN PESHAWAR | publisher=Newsweek Pakistan | accessdate=2014-12-16 | archive-date=2014-12-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141216103436/http://newsweekpakistan.com/taliban-attack-army-run-school-in-peshawar/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>
。

2014年6月起开始，[[巴基斯坦军事|巴基斯坦军方]]在[[北瓦济里斯坦|北瓦济里斯坦]]开展“利剑行动”联合军事攻势，打击该地的暴力势力据点。利剑行动针对6月8日[[卡拉奇|卡拉奇]][[2014年真纳国际机场袭击案|真纳国际机场袭击]]而展开，之后[[巴基斯坦塔利班运动|塔利班]]宣布对事件负责。时值[[巴基斯坦西北部战争|巴基斯坦西北部战争]]，至今已有1200多名恐怖分子被击毙<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/804568/zarb-e-azb-inflicted-fatal-blow-on-terrorists-pm/ |title=Zarb-e-Azb inflicted fatal blow on terrorists: PM |author=Abdul Manan |date=2014-12-10 |publisher=Express Tribune |accessdate=2014-12-17 |archive-date=2019-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106221646/https://tribune.com.pk/story/804568/zarb-e-azb-inflicted-fatal-blow-on-terrorists-pm/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，北瓦济里斯坦90%的地区被肃清<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/791954/zarb-e-azb-army-says-90-of-north-waziristan-cleared/ |title=Zarb-e-Azb: Army says 90% of North Waziristan cleared |date=2014-11-16 |publisher=Express Tribune |accessdate=2014-12-17 |archive-date=2019-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106221549/https://tribune.com.pk/story/791954/zarb-e-azb-army-says-90-of-north-waziristan-cleared/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 经过 ==
上午10时许，六名身着巴基斯坦准军事部队[[边境军|边境军]]服的枪手<ref name="Newsweek Pakistan"/>，从附近的一处墓地潜入学校<ref name="DNA India"/>，缩在墙壁后<ref name="DNA India"/>。进入学校前，枪手向他们开来的[[铃木|铃木]]柏兰ST41面包车纵火。携带自动武器的恐怖分子，径直走向混合中心的礼堂，开枪扫射聚集在学校功能室的儿童<ref name="500held"/>。三军公共关系总干事、巴基斯坦军方公关部的[[阿西·巴杰瓦|阿西·巴杰瓦]]（Asim Bajwa）表示，恐怖分子并不打算挟持任何人质，而是要竭尽所能杀死尽可能多的学生。恐怖分子开火时，许多学生往礼堂另一侧的两个出口跑出，但当中许多人在花园里中枪。

报告亦指出学生被迫目睹包括校长塔希拉·卡兹（Tahira Kazi）在内的教师被活活烧死<ref name="forcedtowatch">{{cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2875729/Up-20-dead-500-children-teachers-taken-hostage-Taliban-gunmen-storm-military-run-school-Pakistan.html/ |title=Children forced to watch their teacher being burned alive as Taliban murder 132 children |date=2014-12-16 |publisher=Daily Mail |accessdate=2014-12-17 |archive-date=2019-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106221640/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2875729/Up-20-dead-500-children-teachers-taken-hostage-Taliban-gunmen-storm-military-run-school-Pakistan.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。过了5-7分钟，陆军[[特勤队|特勤队]]冲进学校，驾驶重型装甲车和卡车从两侧进入。随即，特勤队的人员与恐怖分子交涉，阻止他们继续杀害其他幸存的学生和教员。枪手随后移到学校的管理区，挟持那里的人质，其中一人在礼堂附近被军方击毙，其他六人则设法前往管理区<ref name="Express Tribune">{{cite web |url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/807683/no-hostages-terrorists-wanted-to-inflict-maximum-casualties-says-dg-ispr/ |title=No hostages: Terrorists wanted to inflict maximum casualties, says DG ISPR |date=2014-12-16 |publisher=Express Tribune |accessdate=2014-12-17 |archive-date=2014-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217064915/http://tribune.com.pk/story/807683/no-hostages-terrorists-wanted-to-inflict-maximum-casualties-says-dg-ispr/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。媒体转播车、驾驶[[梅赛德斯-奔驰斯宾特|斯宾特]]（Sprinter）厢式车的创伤急救队，以及医疗单位被军用装甲车载到学校，宪兵队和民警封闭道路，防止恐怖分子逃走<ref name="Express Tribune"/>。

恐怖分子在袭击过程中与上家保持联系，但特勤队攻入不久后，安全部队截获了恐怖分子的通信。“我们知道他们上家的身份，但由于涉及行动，未能公布。他们知道行动地点，必须进行该地区的侦查，而且极有可能在被人揭穿后逃走。”巴杰瓦表示。
=== 伤亡人数 ===
总共1099名学校和教员出现在校舍中，其中960人被反应部队成功解救，但有121人受伤。事件中死亡的145人，包括132名儿童、10名工作人员和3名士兵<ref name="edition.cnn.com"/><ref name="The New York Times"/>。

== 归因 ==
[[巴基斯坦塔利班运动|巴基斯坦塔利班运动]]（TTP）声称对此次袭击事件负责，旨在报复巴基斯坦军方自2014年夏季以来，在北瓦济里斯坦发动的“[[利剑行动|利剑行动]]”军事进攻<ref name="500held">{{cite web| url=http://www.pakistantoday.com.pk/2014/12/16/national/militants-attack-peshawar-school-five-students-injured/| title=TTP militants storm Peshawar school; 131 killed, more than 100 injured| publisher=Pakistan Today| accessdate=2014-12-16| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218181927/http://www.pakistantoday.com.pk/2014/12/16/national/militants-attack-peshawar-school-five-students-injured/| archivedate=2014-12-18}}</ref>。

塔利班发言人穆罕默德·奥马尔·克霍拉桑尼（Muhammad Omar Khorasani）表示：“陆军针对我们的家人，我们就针对小学。我们希望他们能够感受下我们的痛苦。”“我们的6名战士已成功进入陆军学校，我们从外面给他们指示，”<ref>{{cite news|title=TTP claim responsibility for Peshawar school attack|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/807574/ttp-claim-responsibility-for-peshawar-school-attack/|accessdate=2014-12-16|publisher=The Express Tribune|date=2014-12-16|archive-date=2014-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141216120233/http://tribune.com.pk/story/807574/ttp-claim-responsibility-for-peshawar-school-attack/|dead-url=no}}</ref>克霍拉桑尼透过电话表示：“我们的自杀袭击者已进入学校，他们的指示是不伤害孩子，仅针对军方人员。这是针对陆军在北瓦济里斯坦的进攻的复仇。”<ref>{{cite news|title=Police: Taliban attack over, all gunmen killed|url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/asia/2014/12/16/Three-dead-in-Taliban-attack-on-Pakistan-school.html|accessdate=2014-12-17|publisher=Al Arabiya|date=2014-12-17|archive-date=2014-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217214955/http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/asia/2014/12/16/Three-dead-in-Taliban-attack-on-Pakistan-school.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Taliban gunmen hold Pakistan school hostage, kill students|url=http://www.dw.de/taliban-gunmen-hold-pakistan-school-hostage-kill-students/a-18133669|accessdate=2014-12-17|publisher=Deutsche Welle|date=2014-12-17|archive-date=2014-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141216191838/http://www.dw.de/taliban-gunmen-hold-pakistan-school-hostage-kill-students/a-18133669|dead-url=no}}</ref>巴基斯坦[[联邦调查机构|联邦调查机构]]初期侦查显示，该校对由车臣战士阿布·沙塔尔（Abu Shamil）策划领导，伴有3名阿拉伯人，2名来自阿富汗东部讲[[普什图语|普什图语]]的阿富汗人<ref name="Jan Newspapers"/> 。

2014年12月18日，塔利班在其网站发布视频，名为乌马尔·曼苏尔（Umar Mansoor）的男子透露自己是白沙瓦学校袭击案的幕后策划者<ref>{{cite news|title=Umar Mansoor mastermind of Peshawar school attack: TTP|url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1151879|accessdate=2014-12-20|work=DAWN.com|archive-date=2014-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219230517/http://www.dawn.com/news/1151879|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

