== 反应 ==
{{Rquote|right|我决定继续调查白沙瓦案，出面监督行动。这是我的孩子，是我的损失。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hngn.com/articles/52971/20141216/pakistan-prime-minister-nawaz-sharif-children-loss.htm|title=Pakistan Prime Minister Nawaz Sharif: 'These Are My Children And It Is My Loss'|work=Headlines & Global News|accessdate=2014-12-27|archive-date=2019-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190109173617/http://www.hngn.com/articles/52971/20141216/pakistan-prime-minister-nawaz-sharif-children-loss.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>|纳瓦兹·谢里夫|巴基斯坦总理}}
袭击事件在巴基斯坦引起广泛反应，遭到公众、政府、政治和宗教机构、记者和社会科学家的谴责。巴基斯坦媒体对事件反应强烈，许多评论员在各大报章和新闻频道上，呼吁发动更大型和强有力的行动打击武装分子，尤其是塔利班。国际上对袭击的反应也很强烈，许多国家和国际组织纷纷谴责袭击，并向遇难者家属表达慰问。世界各地许多知名人物亦谴责袭击。

总理[[纳瓦兹·谢里夫|纳瓦兹·谢里夫]]谴责本次袭击，称其为“国家的悲剧“，宣布全国哀悼三日，降半旗致哀。总统[[马姆努恩·侯赛因|马姆努恩·侯赛因]]和四省首次部长强烈谴责袭击。

世界各地的艺术家们，亦纷纷表达他们的关切，和对这种可怕行为的愤怒。巴基斯坦歌手谢赫扎德·罗伊·桑伟袭击遇害者写歌，目前是巴基斯坦中央电视频道[[PTV|PTV]]的官方歌曲<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.songshd.pk/2014/12/zindagi-yaad-karti-hai-by-shehzad-roy.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-12-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141222193442/http://www.songshd.pk/2014/12/zindagi-yaad-karti-hai-by-shehzad-roy.html |archivedate=2014-12-22 }}</ref>。

巴基斯坦主要的政治实体谴责袭击，严重谴责对无辜儿童的袭击，强烈要求打击武装分子<ref>{{cite news|title=Political leaders united in sorrow|url=http://www.pakistantoday.com.pk/2014/12/16/national/political-leaders-united-in-sorrow/|accessdate=2014-12-19|work=Pakistan Today|date=2014-12-16|archive-date=2014-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220125606/http://www.pakistantoday.com.pk/2014/12/16/national/political-leaders-united-in-sorrow/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[巴基斯坦正义运动党|巴基斯坦正义运动党]]领袖[[伊姆兰·罕|伊姆兰·罕]]呼吁结束[[自由三月|抗议]]。

[[诺贝尔和平奖|诺贝尔和平奖]]得主[[马拉拉·优素福扎伊|马拉拉·优素福扎伊]]谴责此次袭击，并在声明中表示：“我对白沙瓦恐袭这种摆在我们面前的毫无意义的冷血行为，感到伤心欲绝<ref>{{cite web|title=Heartbroken by senseless and cold blooded act of terror: Malala Yousafzai|url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/peshawar-massacre-malala-yousafzai-pakistan-taliban-senseless-cold-blooded-act-of-terror/1/407157.html|work=India Today|accessdate=2014-12-16|archive-date=2019-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190109173608/https://www.indiatoday.in/world/story/peshawar-massacre-malala-yousafzai-pakistan-taliban-senseless-cold-blooded-act-of-terror-231428-2014-12-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”她的父亲，齐亚乌丁·优素福扎伊表示，他的心在流血，家人们都笼罩在白沙瓦校园惨案的阴影中<ref>{{cite web|title=Heart is bleeding: Ziauddin Yousafzai|url=http://www.floridanewstime.com/national/85920-malala-yousafzai-s-father-says-his-heart-is-bleeding-over-peshawar-school-massacre.html|work=Florida News Time|accessdate=2014-12-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219195114/http://www.floridanewstime.com/national/85920-malala-yousafzai-s-father-says-his-heart-is-bleeding-over-peshawar-school-massacre.html|archivedate=2014-12-19}}</ref>。

即便是[[基地组织|基地组织]]的发言人，也对事件感到心痛，认为士兵针对的不应该是孩子<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://m.ibnlive.com/news/alqaeda-bursting-with-pain-over-pakistan-school-attack/519210-56.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-12-27 |archive-date=2014-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141228174551/http://m.ibnlive.com/news/alqaeda-bursting-with-pain-over-pakistan-school-attack/519210-56.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

经中国和巴基斯坦两军高层安排，2015年2月和3月，白沙瓦陆军学校学生代表团分两批赴华疗养。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.chinanews.com/mil/2015/03-06/7107537.shtml |title=巴基斯坦遭袭击军校学生将赴中国旅行疗养，中国新闻网，2015-03-06 |accessdate=2015-04-21 |archive-date=2015-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717204817/http://www.chinanews.com/mil/2015/03-06/7107537.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 后续 ==
[[File:Candlelight_vigil_in_London_for_the_victims_of_the_Peshawar_school_siege..jpg|thumb]]
许多国际媒体组织称此次袭击是巴基斯坦的“911<ref>{{cite news|title=Peshawar school massacre: 'This is Pakistan's 9/11 – now is the time to act'|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/dec/19/peshawar-school-massacre-pakistans-911|accessdate=2014-12-20|publisher=Guardian|date=2014-12-17|archive-date=2014-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220062213/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/dec/19/peshawar-school-massacre-pakistans-911|dead-url=no}}</ref>”。袭击不久后，流行观点对塔利班表示愤怒。巴基斯坦政府和军队对事件表现出及时反应<ref name="Reuters, 2014">{{cite news|title=After Peshawar school massacre, watch for the gloves to come off|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/808229/after-peshawar-school-massacre-watch-for-the-gloves-to-come-off/|accessdate=2014-12-17|agency=Reuters|work=The Express Tribune|publisher=date=17 December 2014|archive-date=2014-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217181035/http://tribune.com.pk/story/808229/after-peshawar-school-massacre-watch-for-the-gloves-to-come-off/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

伊朗裔美籍学者瓦利·纳斯尔表示，“塔利班意图削弱军队的意志，认为军事进攻需投入大量人力成本，借此让公众给军队创造压力，从而撤回进攻，但实际上遭到他们反弹<ref name="Reuters, 2014"/>。”

袭击后第二天，纳瓦兹·谢里夫，對策划恐袭案件的暂缓死刑被解除<ref>{{cite news|title=Govt lifts moratorium on capital punishment|url=http://www.dailytimes.com.pk/national/18-Dec-2014/govt-lifts-moratorium-on-capital-punishment|accessdate=2014-12-20|work=[[Daily_Times|Daily Times]]|publisher=Asim Qadeer Rana|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220053419/http://www.dailytimes.com.pk/national/18-Dec-2014/govt-lifts-moratorium-on-capital-punishment|archivedate=2014-12-20}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Pakistan lifts moratorium on death penalty after Taliban attack|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/Pakistan-lifts-moratorium-on-death-penalty-after-Taliban-attack/articleshow/45546231.cms|accessdate=2014-12-20|work=[[Times_of_India|Times of India]]|archive-date=2014-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220140427/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/Pakistan-lifts-moratorium-on-death-penalty-after-Taliban-attack/articleshow/45546231.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。随后，穆罕默德·阿基尔与艾尔沙德·马哈茂德，此前因暗杀前总统[[佩尔韦兹·穆沙拉夫|佩尔韦兹·穆沙拉夫]]未遂而被判刑，於12月19日被处决<ref>{{cite news|title=Pakistan makes final preparations to hang two terrorists|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/Pakistan-makes-final-preparations-to-hang-two-terrorists/articleshow/45575786.cms|accessdate=2014-12-19|publisher=Times of India|date=2014-12-19|archive-date=2014-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220132731/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/Pakistan-makes-final-preparations-to-hang-two-terrorists/articleshow/45575786.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Pakistan resumes executions after Peshawar school attack|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-30556260|accessdate=2014-12-20|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|archive-date=2014-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219231108/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-30556260|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 解除恐怖分子的暂缓处决 ===
2014年12月17日，总理[[纳瓦兹·谢里夫|纳瓦兹·谢里夫]]签署文件，解除接触涉及恐怖袭击案件的暂缓死刑<ref name="The News International, 2014">{{cite news|last1=Web edition|title=Pakistan to end death penalty moratorium in terror cases|url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/article-168932-Pakistan-to-end-death-penalty-moratorium-in-terror-cases|accessdate=2014-12-17|agency=The News International|publisher=The News International, 2014|date=2014-12-17|archive-date=2014-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217120428/http://www.thenews.com.pk/article-168932-Pakistan-to-end-death-penalty-moratorium-in-terror-cases|dead-url=no}}</ref>。总理秘书处表示：“总理已批准取消恐袭案的暂缓处决。”<ref name="The News International, 2014"/>巴基斯坦自2008年已停用死刑，目前约有800人恐怖分子被关押在巴基斯坦的死囚牢<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia/2014/12/pakistan-lifts-death-penalty-moratorium-2014121710537499387.html |title=Pakistan lifts death penalty moratorium |date=2014-12-17 |publisher=Aljazeera |accessdate=2014-12-18 |archive-date=2014-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141222044704/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia/2014/12/pakistan-lifts-death-penalty-moratorium-2014121710537499387.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此举后来被人们普遍认为是巴基斯坦从未将恐怖分子归案。多数时候，法官和证人都不敢挺身而出，裁决恐怖分子的刑期。甚至已定罪的恐怖分子被送往监狱，也会借助巴基斯坦治安体系的脆弱点越狱<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/365064/prison-break-militants-attack-bannu-jail-over-900-inmates-freed/ |title=Prison break: Taliban attack Bannu jail, nearly 400 inmates escape |date=2012-04-15 |publisher=The Express Tribune |accessdate=2014-12-18 |archive-date=2014-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218170226/http://tribune.com.pk/story/365064/prison-break-militants-attack-bannu-jail-over-900-inmates-freed/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其中不乏[[本努|本努]]和[[德拉·伊斯梅尔·汗|德拉·伊斯梅尔·汗]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1032777 |title=Pakistani Taliban free over 175 inmates in DI Khan jailbreak |date=2013-07-30 |publisher=DAWN |accessdate=2014-12-18 |archive-date=2019-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403052559/https://www.dawn.com/news/1032777 |dead-url=no }}</ref>等高调的恐怖分子。

[[国际特赦组织|国际特赦组织]]亚太区副主任[[大卫·格里菲斯|大卫·格里菲斯]]对这一决定表示反对，他表示：“诉诸死亡并不是问题的答案——永远不是。答案应是政府集中力量，而非用恢复处决来延续暴力的恶性循环<ref>{{cite news|title=Pakistan: Resuming executions 'not the answer' to Peshawar school tragedy|url=http://www.amnesty.org/en/news/pakistan-resuming-executions-not-answer-peshawar-school-tragedy-2014-12-17|accessdate=2014-12-17|publisher=Amnesty International|date=2014-12-17|archive-date=2015-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150210022533/http://www.amnesty.org/en/news/pakistan-resuming-executions-not-answer-peshawar-school-tragedy-2014-12-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

