== 打击 ==
===出动无人机===
袭击发生后，[[无人机|无人机]]准备发动针对恐怖分子的空袭，而巴基斯坦空军当前的任务，则是追捕塔利班头目穆拉赫·法兹卢拉，法兹卢拉在11月25日的无人机打击中侥幸逃脱<ref>{{cite news|title=TTP leader Mullah Fazlullah escapes US drone strike near Pak-Afghan border|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/796877/ttp-leader-fazlullah-escapes-us-drone-strike-near-pak-afghan-border/|accessdate=2014-12-21|archive-date=2014-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220101855/http://tribune.com.pk/story/796877/ttp-leader-fazlullah-escapes-us-drone-strike-near-pak-afghan-border/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。12月17日，巴空军的[[F-16战隼战斗机|F-16战机]]和[[枭龙战机|JF-17雷电战机]]，在阿富汗边境附近的57名恐怖分子的藏身地提拉谷（Tirah Valley）投下炸弹。另外二十架战机执行动态目标空中轰炸任务<ref>{{cite news|last1=staff writer|title=Live: 57 terrorists killed, as air force launches retaliatory strikes in Tirah Valley|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/808157/live-nation-mourns-141-lives-lost-in-peshawar-school-attack/|accessdate=2014-12-17|date=2014-12-17|archive-date=2014-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217133236/http://tribune.com.pk/story/808157/live-nation-mourns-141-lives-lost-in-peshawar-school-attack/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。12月16日，一架[[美国中央情报局|美国中央情报局]]无人机，在阿富汗东部杀死4名塔利班武装分子<ref>{{cite news|title=Dec 16 drone strike in Afghanistan killed four TTP militants: Afghan official|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/808163/dec-16-drone-strike-in-afghanistan-killed-four-ttp-militants-afghan-official/|accessdate=2014-12-20|date=2014-12-17|archive-date=2014-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217173639/http://tribune.com.pk/story/808163/dec-16-drone-strike-in-afghanistan-killed-four-ttp-militants-afghan-official/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。12月20日，另一架无人机在北瓦济里斯坦击毙5名恐怖分子，官员表示死亡人数预计将上升<ref>{{cite news|title=Drone strike kills five suspected militants in North Waziristan|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/809754/drone-strike-kills-four-suspected-militants-in-datta-khel/|accessdate=2014-12-20|archive-date=2014-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220105758/http://tribune.com.pk/story/809754/drone-strike-kills-four-suspected-militants-in-datta-khel/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。与此同时，据报道大约21名塔利班恐怖分子在[[开伯尔特区|开伯尔特区]]击毙，他们试图在巴空军的打击下逃离阿富汗<ref>{{cite news|last1=AFP|title=21 militants killed in Khyber Agency|url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/article-169241-Air-strikes-kill-21-militants-in-Khyber-Agency|accessdate=2014-12-20|archive-date=2014-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220180345/http://www.thenews.com.pk/article-169241-Air-strikes-kill-21-militants-in-Khyber-Agency|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年12月20日，一份未经证实的报告指出，法兹卢拉被巴空军战机在阿富汗击毙<ref name=oneindia>{{Cite web |url=http://www.oneindia.com/international/ttp-chief-fazlullah-killed-pakistan-media-peshawar-siege-1598251.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-12-21 |archive-date=2014-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141221035909/http://www.oneindia.com/international/ttp-chief-fazlullah-killed-pakistan-media-peshawar-siege-1598251.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===定点清除塔利班===
执法机关和警察全国追捕武装分子，并针对塔利班武装分子的报道，已在电视新闻媒体广泛流传。袭击发生后，巴基斯坦情报机构在[[奎达|奎达]]追踪到3名塔利班武装分子，并在其逃往阿富汗前逮捕。卡拉奇都會區警方和犯罪调查局人员曾与塔利班头目阿比德·迈查尔（Abid Macchar，绰号蚊子阿比德）相遇，警方追至穆沙拉夫殖民地，将其和三个同伙击毙。在卡拉奇的单独行动中，犯罪调查局小队在霍克斯湾高速公路追击并逮捕基地组织南亚分支的五名成员，九月份，他们涉嫌策划在卡拉奇海军造船厂发动袭击。12月20日，巴基斯坦特警小队袭击了卡拉奇曼霍佩尔区一间安全屋，枪战中击毙五名塔利班<ref>{{cite news|title=Rangers kill three ‘terrorists’ in Karachi shootout|url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/article-169225-Rangers-kill-three-terrorists-in-Karachi-shootout--|accessdate=2014-12-20|archive-date=2014-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220180348/http://www.thenews.com.pk/article-169225-Rangers-kill-three-terrorists-in-Karachi-shootout--|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

12月20日下午，[[开伯尔-普赫图赫瓦省|开伯尔-普赫图赫瓦省]]警方和FIA特伍搜查白沙瓦以北30公里一处城镇的一所安全屋。在安全屋的交火中，开伯尔警方和其他执法机构击毙包括指挥官在内的六名塔利班，连同另外两个高价值目标<ref name="Dunya News">{{cite news|last1=News Desk|title=Six militants killed in Peshawar operation|url=http://dunyanews.tv/index.php/en/Pakistan/250949-Six-militants-killed-in-Peshawar-operation|accessdate=2014-12-20|agency=Dunya News|publisher=Dunya News|date=2014-12-20|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912032614/http://dunyanews.tv/en/Pakistan/250949-Six-militants-killed-in-Peshawar-operation|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===阿富汗和ISAF介入===
12月17日，巴基斯坦军方总参谋长拉赫尔·谢里夫将军，在[[巴基斯坦三军情报局|三军情报局]]总干事利兹万·阿赫塔尔的陪同下，在喀布尔会见了阿富汗总统[[阿什拉夫·加尼·艾哈迈德扎伊|阿什拉夫·加尼·艾哈迈德扎伊]]，以及美军和北约驻阿富汗部队指挥官[[约翰·坎贝尔_(美军上将)|约翰·F·坎贝尔]]。据巴基斯坦消息人士透露，拉赫尔将军用塔利班头目作为交换，要求阿富汗政府对其境内的塔利班藏身所采取打击行动<ref>{{cite news|title=Pakistani Army Chief Asks Afghans to Help Find Taliban Commanders Behind Massacre|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/18/world/asia/pakistan-premier-lifts-death-penalty-moratorium-following-school-massacre.html?_r=0|accessdate=2014-12-17|publisher=New York Times|date=2014-12-17|archive-date=2014-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217215716/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/18/world/asia/pakistan-premier-lifts-death-penalty-moratorium-following-school-massacre.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。与阿方官员会谈时，拉赫尔向阿富汗国民军参谋长[[谢尔·穆罕默德·卡里米|谢尔·穆罕默德·卡里米]]传达消息，“采取果断行动打击塔利班避难所，否则巴基斯坦就会介入。”情报官员证实了传达给阿总统的消息，称其警告阿富汗政府“此番不采取行动，我们将探讨所有的可能，包括军事介入。”在进一步的会谈中，拉赫尔将军告诉阿富汗总统：“巴军方有权肃清塔利班在[[库纳尔省|库纳尔省]]和[[努尔斯坦省|努尔斯坦省]]的避难所，但因阿富汗主权和领土完整而克制。加尼向拉赫尔保证，国家将采取一切必要手段铲除恐怖分子。阿富汗领导人也讨论了针对塔利班的联合行动<ref name=Tribune,>{{cite news|last1=Yousaf|first1=Kamran|title=Kabul, ISAF promise action against TTP sanctuaries|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/808780/kabul-isaf-promise-action-against-ttp-sanctuaries/|accessdate=2014-12-17|agency=Tribune,|publisher=Tribune,|date=2014-12-18|archive-date=2014-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218020542/http://tribune.com.pk/story/808780/kabul-isaf-promise-action-against-ttp-sanctuaries/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据《民族》杂志报道，总理纳瓦兹·谢里夫向阿富汗总统发布“介入”的独立声明，并向喀布尔发布消息，强调“清剿塔利班是我们共同的愿望<ref name="THe Nation, Kabul desk">{{cite news|last1=Chaudhry|title=COAS warns Kabul of hot pursuit|url=http://nation.com.pk/editors-picks/18-Dec-2014/coas-warns-kabul-of-hot-pursuit|accessdate=2014-12-19|agency=THe Nation, Kabul desk|publisher=THe Nation, Kabul desk|date=2014-12-17|archive-date=2014-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218172049/http://nation.com.pk/editors-picks/18-Dec-2014/coas-warns-kabul-of-hot-pursuit|dead-url=no}}</ref>”。

巴军方目前正抓紧搜捕<ref name="The News International, editorial">{{cite news|last1=Abbasi|first1=Ansar|title=Hunt for wanted militants|url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/Todays-News-13-34784-Hunt-for-wanted-militants|accessdate=2014-12-20|agency=The News International, editorial|publisher=The News International, editorialnational, editorial|date=2014-12-20|location=Islamabad, Pakistan|archive-date=2014-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220180352/http://www.thenews.com.pk/Todays-News-13-34784-Hunt-for-wanted-militants|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Dawn news, Khyber Agency desk">{{cite news|last1=AFP|title=Top Uzbek commander among 17 terrorists killed in Khyber air strikes|url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1151682/top-uzbek-commander-among-17-terrorists-killed-in-khyber-air-strikes|accessdate=2014-12-19|agency=Dawn news, Khyber Agency desk|publisher=Dawn news, Khyber Agency desk|date=2014-12-19|archive-date=2014-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218231044/http://www.dawn.com/news/1151682/top-uzbek-commander-among-17-terrorists-killed-in-khyber-air-strikes|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Dawn news. 18 December 2014"/> 。12月18日晚，巴陆军部队尾随逃跑的恐怖分子，立刻在开伯尔和提拉谷同时发动地面进攻，以防恐怖分子逃亡阿富汗<ref name="Dawn news. 18 December 2014">{{cite news|last1=Zahir Shah Sherazi|first1=Zahir Shah|title=Drone strike kills eight militants on Khyber Agency border|url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1151855/drone-strike-kills-eight-militants-on-khyber-agency-border|accessdate=2014-12-19|agency=Dawn news|publisher=Dawn news. 18 December 2014|date=2014-12-18|archive-date=2014-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219122839/http://www.dawn.com/news/1151855/drone-strike-kills-eight-militants-on-khyber-agency-border|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在突袭中，据报一些恐怖分子已经逃出，身后留下同伙的尸体，尸体照片在社交媒体中流传<ref name="Dawn news. 18 December 2014"/>。当晚在开伯尔特区的单独空袭中，巴空军战斗机据报猎杀一名最高指挥官和17名试图逃亡阿富汗的恐怖分子<ref name="Dawn, Khyber">{{cite news|last1=AFP|title=Top Uzbek commander among 17 terrorists killed in Khyber air strikes|url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1151682/top-uzbek-commander-among-17-terrorists-killed-in-khyber-air-strikes|accessdate=2014-12-19|agency=Dawn, Khyber|publisher=Dawn, Khyber|date=2014-12-19|archive-date=2014-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218231044/http://www.dawn.com/news/1151682/top-uzbek-commander-among-17-terrorists-killed-in-khyber-air-strikes|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

